												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "~Astarion smiles, turns and lays the player down on the ground in one motion. Kissing their player on their chest, then the side of their rib. The player turns onto their side and Astarion slides in behind, ending with one long, kiss on the small of their neck before slideing his hand over the spot he kissed and inserting himself. The player responds with pleasure and their hand comes up to cover Astarions. Cut wide to show the imbrace, then a cloud passing over the moon."
												}
											},
