												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "~The player pushes off the tree, Astarion topples landing on his back--the player still on top. The player pulls their neck to one side, baring it. Astarion is almost flustered as his appetite kicks in. He rolls the player beneath him and bites down and the player's eyes shoot up, looking at the moon through the trees."
